Regulation No 110  of  the  Economic Commission for  Europe of  the  United Nations (UNECE) —  Uniform provisions concerning the approval of: 
I.   specific  components of  motor  vehicles using  compressed natural gas  (CNG) and/or liquefied  natural gas (LNG) in their propulsion system; 
II. vehicles with  regard to  the  installation of  specific  components of  an  approved  type  for  the  use  of compressed natural gas (CNG) and/or liquefied natural gas (LNG) in their propulsion system [2015/999].
